metadata.description:
Unique 4775 x 7457 pixel art piece. Code-generated by my second generative art engine created in 2007.
Generative timestamp 2007-02-13_8:56pm.

What started as a hand-coded music-reactive and semi-random art installation became a well-known early generative art + street art blend, mentioned in several early books and publications on generative art, when this art form was just getting started.
